title: Mayor’s Charity Ball raises almost $20,000 for local charities (Bundaberg Regional Council)
text: ( Source : Bundaberg Regional Council ) There'll be no masking the joy of four local charities who are the recipients of almost $20, 000 , raised at the 2015 Mayor 's Charity Ball . Mayor Cr Mal Forman said he was thrilled with the fundraising
